    "body": "I think the main issue here is that we ship a custom version of a system library (`argparse`), and this is prone to fail if `argparse` is imported before we hack `sys.path` internally.\r\n\r\nProbably a better solution would be not to customize argparse, but instead have a wrapper on top of whatever the system provides.",
